<bblocks://dde.bbr.metadata.DDEproperties.ddeServiceInfo> a skos:Concept,
        dcat:Dataset,
        bblocks:BBlock,
        bblocks:Schema ;
    rdfs:label "DDE Service Information Properties" ;
    dct:abstract "Conditional extension for service resources. Implements SV_ServiceIdentification (DDE spec Table 2): serviceType (mandatory), containsOperations, accessProperties, operatedDataset, and endpointDescription. Defines properties: schema:distribution, schema:dataset, schema:additionalProperty. Uses building blocks: additionalProperty (schemaorgProperties), definedTerm (schemaorgProperties), identifier (schemaorgProperties)."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
