        bblocks:Schema ;
    rdfs:label "DDE Geographic Dataset Properties" ;
    dct:abstract "Conditional extension for geographic dataset resources. Implements MD_SpatialRepresentation (DDE spec Table 5): mandatory spatialCoverage, plus spatialRepresentationType, spatialResolution, referenceSystemType, and referenceSystemIdentifier. Defines properties: schema:spatialCoverage, schema:additionalProperty. Uses building blocks: spatialExtent (schemaorgProperties), additionalProperty (schemaorgProperties), identifier (schemaorgProperties)."^^<https://www.w3.org/ns/iana/media-types/text/markdown> ;
